Karitane
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a) the name given to Plunket Society hospitals and family support units. b) a nurse trained by the Plunket Society for the care of babies and preschoolers. 1. Short form of Karitane nurse, named from the Otago bay and Truby King's house there.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
